Interface SVGAnimatedPathData is not fully implemented, according to the SVG 1.1
recomendation. The following methods that return lists are not implemented and
throw a Runtime Exeption, in class: org.apache.batik.dom.svg.SVGOMAnimatedPathData:
    public SVGPathSegList getAnimatedNormalizedPathSegList()
    public SVGPathSegList getAnimatedPathSegList()
    public SVGPathSegList getNormalizedPathSegList()
